   <div class="teaser_fmt"> 
    <h3>DVT</h3> 
    <p>Deep vein thrombosis, or DVT, is caused by a blood clot in a deep vein and can be life-threatening. Symptoms may include swelling, pain, and tenderness, often in the legs. Risk factors include immobility, hormone therapy, and pregnancy. </p> 
